## 🛠 Recommended Preprocessing Pipeline

1. N4 Bias Field Correction  
2. Intensity Normalization (Z-score per volume)  
3. Resampling to isotropic resolution  
4. 3D Patch Extraction  
5. Data Augmentation (flip, rotation, elastic deformation)  

---

## 📊 Evaluation Metrics

Common evaluation metrics used in BraTS challenge:

- Dice Similarity Coefficient (DSC)  
- Hausdorff Distance (HD95)  
- Sensitivity  
- Specificity  

